name: Gmail
itemDescription:
To run this importer you need a to fill in an email address and an app password below, and enable IMAP in your email settings, for gmail that is under 
https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/#settings/fwdandpop 
The recommended usage is with an app password, for which you need to enable 2FA (Google), which you can do under Security at 
https://myaccount.google.com/security

name: Geolocation indexer

name: Note Label Indexer
itemDescription: This indexer extracts labels from notes. You can specify aliases in the labels to add keywords that are used to match against.

name: Note List Indexer
itemDescription: This indexer extracts lists from notes. It detects both structured and unstructured lists

title: A demo note
content:
Hi there,

Let's explore the new text editor.

  • This is a list

  • You can press return to make a new item

    • Indented item

    • Something else

Or an ordered list:

  1. Milk

  2. Eggs

  3. Flour

    1. Self-raising

    2. Plain

Todo list

  • Try out new editor

  • Finish writing blog post

    • Improve the second paragraph

  • Prepare presentation

It also supports both inline code and code blocks:

def some_function(argument):
    return "Automatic code highlighting!"
